margins disagCat, eydx(Trend) grand coefl post
nlcom ("Trend_disagCat0":_b[Trend:0bn.disagCat]*100) ("Trend_disagCat1":_b[Trend:1.disagCat]*100) ("Trend_Pooled":_b[Trend:_cons]*100), post
